manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: TRANSMART M3 Cordless Vacuum Cleaner TRANSMART cordless vacuum cleaner is equipped with 250W upgrade motors, providing a powerful 24 Kpa suction power to capture pet hair, cat litter, dirt and other chaotic debris whether on the carpet or floor. This stick vacuum cleaner has 6 adjustable suction levels and a long runtime battery up to 50 mins.

Easily Clean Dust from High Places The 2-in-1 brush can be directly connected to the main unit of the vacuum cleaner to facilitate direct cleaning of bookshelves, wardrobes, tabletops and other high places. Clean up Junk in Gaps Install a long-mouth brush head to clean dust, small garbage and dog hair in the gaps between the sofa and bed. It can also be used to clean various hard-to-reach corners to make your living environment cleaner. Easy to Maneuver TRANSMART vacuum cleaner's 90°180° flexible LED stick brush with strong LED headlights can easily adjust the angle to clean particles and dust in dark places.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best Vacuum Ever!
reviews.reviewText: I haven’t used an actual vacuum in like seven years, so what I was expecting was not this thin, little, lightweight machine. They slashed the price after it was in my cart, so I scooped it up quick! It’s definitely worth it. Super easy to assemble, and it holds a charge very well. I use it on carpet and LVT floor (after sweeping). It picks up everything! It’s very fluid and agile, too. Dumping the waste is literally the click of a button. Gone are the days of big, bulky vacuums with bags and long cords! The only thing I wish was that it had an extension to make it taller. If you are over 5’7” you might get a cramp easily from having to lean so much.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best stick vac I have purchased by far
reviews.reviewText: I bought this when it was on a deep discount and did not even need it because I already have two others. This thing is awesome. I have six cats and the amount of fur this gets out of the rug is unreal. The best part about this for me is it actually looks like you vacuumed with a full size vacuum.. the suction is very good and even pulls up the piles in the carpet. Having the suction strength options is also key because I'm able to now vacuum my bathroom rugs without them getting stuck up into the beater brush. Super glad I purchased this!

reviews.reviewText: This stick vacuum's suction power is mind-blowing! It devours dirt and debris with ease, leaving my floors spotless. I'm genuinely impressed by its performance – it's like having a professional cleaner at home! Love it and highly recommend.
